text: Miaenia fujiyamai is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Shōnen Matsumura and Masaki Matsushita in 1933." Miaenia fujiyamai (Matsumura & Matsushita, 1933) ". BioLib. Retrieved 12 August 2020. ==References== Category:Miaenia Category:Beetles described in 1933
title: Miaenia fujiyamai
